        B) Emit all three Task tool calls in a single coordinator response for parallel execution<br>
        C) Create a sequential pipeline where each subagent passes results to the next<br>
        D) Use fork_session to create three independent branches</p>
        <button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Reveal Answer</button>
        <div class="answer-reveal"><strong>B.</strong> Parallel spawning via multiple Task calls in a single response minimises latency.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="exam-question">
        <p><strong>Q5.</strong> A synthesis subagent produces claims without source attribution, despite the web search agent returning well-sourced results. What is the most likely cause?</p>
