        B) The web search results were passed as raw text without structured metadata separating claims from sources<br>
        C) The synthesis agent has a bug in its output formatting<br>
        D) The coordinator is not aggregating results correctly</p>
        <button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Reveal Answer</button>
