        B) Implement a tool call interception hook that blocks the transfer tool until screening completes<br>
        C) Add few-shot examples showing the correct screening workflow<br>
        D) Implement a PostToolUse hook that flags unscreened transfers</p>
        <button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Reveal Answer</button>
